  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "In a large bowl, mix the vanilla sugar, flour, and cold butter until crumbly.",
    "Press the crumble mixture into the bottom of a 9x13 inch baking dish.",
    "In a separate bowl, mix the granulated sugar and baking beans.",
    "Pour the bean mixture over the crumble layer.",
    "Sprinkle the oat topping over the bean mixture.",
    "Bake for 40-45 minutes or until the topping is golden brown.",
    "Remove from oven and sprinkle matcha powder on top.",
    "Let cool completely before serving."
